Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能够如此轻易地躲开这利桩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这个世界上恐怕也就只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,红方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:13.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,原来如此 你正是适合阻挡在此地之王面前的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不敢当 异国的王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然后我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:23.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,对你来说 这利桩既是攻击 又是防御
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,既是示威 也是恐怖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,稳定领地 稳定居城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,稳定应当守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:37.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也就是说 你想要仅凭自己形成一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这是靠对祖国的爱完成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,还是出自身为王的责任感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是想揭露余的内心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是异国的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这里并没有你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,王也许是孤高的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:02.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是也不存在没有麾下单独上战场的王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然后 我是英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便与一国为敌也无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,独自与这国家为敌也无所畏惧吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不愧是英雄！ 不愧是余的敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 你早已在余的死亡陷阱之内！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很遗憾 余的宝具的本质并非「利桩」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,刺出的利桩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这一概念本身就是宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:44.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,只要你还在余的领域之内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就无法逃离这个宝具！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,来吧 结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,红方的Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:13.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,火焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈这就是叛逆！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,叛逆就是我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:05.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,很好 再多来一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,再对来一些！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他叛逆的精神化作实体的姿态！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾辈的大纲并没出错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:28.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,还真有如此恐怖的宝具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:28.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那正是「疵兽的咆吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31\pos(696,600)}Crying Warmonger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,能够将受到的伤害变换为魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,并化作自己的力量的宝具！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴达克斯既是剑斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:44.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也是为被虐待的人们挺身而出的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他的生存方式在成为从者后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,便被升华成为了那宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 虽说能将伤痛化作力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也并非无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,极限已经近在眼前了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:05.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那位大英雄马上就会放出一生最强的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然后消失了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.70,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,接着那正是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我们御主的革命剧的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的铁拳即是爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,来吧！ 接受我的爱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:28.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,休想逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:50.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在那里吗 压政者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:57.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那个方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真是烦人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你这样的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已经是对骑士王的侮辱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齐格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,已经到极限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,齐格！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你的身体…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,虽然不懂怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不过已经要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,反正说到底不过是赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:40.60,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是不可能敌得过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,红方的Berserker？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:50.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,压政者啊 在我的爱中毁灭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你这 肮脏的肉球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,Saber 快点撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,立刻离开那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:15.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那家伙非常不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好… 好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要动 伤口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那边的两位 请快逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这里很危险 快一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你是… 为什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.77,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明明这条命是你救回来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:46.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 我觉得 无论如何都得这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:48.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.27,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要责怪他！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,他是为了保护身临险境的我而战斗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,然后才会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必须快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不 我已经动不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你才应该快点离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你不是应该在这里毁灭的从者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那么 起码黑方的Ri…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:15.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:16.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不要不要不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你也不是小孩子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我说不要就是不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也不能逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果Ruler是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,也不会把他丢在这里逃走吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,唉 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你都这么说了也就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:42.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我也有不能逃离这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,请不要离开这里 绝对！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,斯巴达克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我不能让你这样的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,伤害无辜的民众
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,时机已到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的一击将破坏所有的压制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,粉碎所有的权力！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这就是斯巴达克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我的旗帜啊 请守护我的同胞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,吾的神明在此！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Luminosite Eternlle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:18.71,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 还活着 得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,好疼… 请让开一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:27.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,各位都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:28.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.97,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,死在这里吧 Lancer！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大地啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,太慢了！ 天空啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,墙壁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,宝具吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,梵天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,{\fs31}Brahma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,御主正在召集我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,下次再决一胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么？ 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:47.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,达尼克吗… 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:53.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:14:59.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:11.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,难道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,真没想到居然还有这样的手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,现在 长久以来一直守护的尤格多米雷尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,被逼入了绝境… 这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:02.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 这种程度的苦境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在这百年来 已经有过无数次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,八十年前 尤格多米雷尼亚得到衰落的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,无法再次作为魔术师出人头地的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我参加了冬木的圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,利用了国家与军队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有时甚至连协助者都被我当成弃子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,为了延长寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不断吞噬他人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,现在就连我自己都不知道自己是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便如此 我也要得到大圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:41.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎么可能又会将其交给别人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,难以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:46.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,大圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:50.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,如果是从者就能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是我们所彼此争夺的大圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看来我必须得去一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:07.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这将是质问红方的最后机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:12.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之后我会好好说教齐格你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.30,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我明白了 我会做好心理准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看来这边还没有探知术式的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.92,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,看来 来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.12,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.20,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,省得余去找你了 红方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,刚才失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:08.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,就在这里重新战斗 来对你尽到礼数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你要由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,这次余一定会将你刺成串的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,怎么了？ 黑方的Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.52,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,跟刚才不一样 动作里缺乏精彩之处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.57,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,孤高的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.17,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在救援到来之前要休息吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便与多人作战我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:23.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,什么…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余的力量在这难道行不通吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:45.15,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,还是魔力的供给被抑制了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.02,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是红方的Lancer啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:53.22,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余即便赌上龙公之名也要击败你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:00.67,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.55,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那里是红方的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,无法完全发挥身为王的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:09.82,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,是赢不了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:13.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,达尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:14.95,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,你知道关于余的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,不逊又令人极为不快的传说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.87,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,后世之人总是对死者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,擅自抱有幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,没错 总是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 余绝对无法原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,玷污余之一族的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:45.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,将余光荣的生存方式笼罩上阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:49.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,即便是后世 也永远应当被定罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,正是如此 王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.35,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,延续家名是我们的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:01.00,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,决不能允许被卑劣之人擅自伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,赌上瓦拉几亚大公的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.05,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,必须防止进一步的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.42,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,因此余要托付给圣杯的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:14.85,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,那就是将那口口相传的肮脏的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,从余的历史中抹消…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:19.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,遵命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.45,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,所以必须要赢得这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.40,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是达尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.62,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,虽然你也应该明白 但还是要多加提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:31.47,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,绝对不要让余使用「那个」宝具…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.90,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,哪怕要难看地败北
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.65,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,余也绝对不会使用「那个」宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.72,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,若是你使用令咒强迫余的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.07,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,之后的事 就不必我多说了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.25,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,明白了「吾王」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.37,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,但是 既然如此就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.32,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,应当守护的是尤格多米雷尼亚的存续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:02.10,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,应当到达的是「根源的漩涡」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.80,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,无论如何都需要大圣杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.75,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,抱歉了Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.50,Default-CN,,0,0,60,,我要打出王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.85,Default-CN,,0,0,0,,第11话 永远的光辉
